item.title: Sue Wallace
item.description: Senior Statistician with 5 years of experience working as a statistician and analyst in the charity and public sector. Working across three governmental departments I have deployed my analytical and data science skills in fast paced environments to produce statistical publications, drive reproducibility in analytics, provide projections and insight to policy colleagues, and provide training in the use of R via a series of self - developed workshops.
